Earlier in the park,

5
00:01:57,530 --> 00:02:00,140
we didn't finish our conversation.

6
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:04,020
I came here now because some things

7
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:06,200
are just between the two of us.

8
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:09,759
I want to speak to you alone.

9
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:16,230
Go ahead.

10
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:19,650
The journal I sent you

11
00:02:19,650 --> 00:02:23,680
didn't include words such as "I like you."

12
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:27,280
How can it be considered a love letter?

13
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:31,939
I only sent you the journal 
 because Chun Lu died.

14
00:02:31,939 --> 00:02:36,259
 Jiang Qiao Xi, 
 can Chun Lu be your daughter? 

15
00:02:36,259 --> 00:02:38,400
 I want to call her Jiang Chun Lu. 

16
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,960
 Even in a very distant provincial city, 

17
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:43,980
 you must remember you have a daughter. 

18
00:02:43,980 --> 00:02:49,680
 Jiang Chun Lu, from now on, 
 you will be Jiang Chun Lu. 

19
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:52,120
 Be good and wait for Daddy to come back. 

20
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:54,619
 You're so childish, Jiang Qiao Xi. 

21
00:02:54,619 --> 00:02:57,779
I gave Chun Lu to you as a daughter, 
 only as a make-believe game.

22
00:02:57,779 --> 00:03:00,320
Chun Lu is my daughter.

23
00:03:01,510 --> 00:03:03,680
She has nothing to do with you.

24
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:08,599
At first, I only wanted to write an obituary,

25
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:11,020
but then I added some things about Qunshan.

26
00:03:11,020 --> 00:03:13,860
 I remembered when you were little, 

27
00:03:13,860 --> 00:03:17,099
 you said you liked Qunshan 
 and didn't want to leave. 

28
00:03:17,099 --> 00:03:21,960
 Actually, I worry the same 
 about all the children that come to Qunshan. 

29
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:25,700
 There's nothing special about you. 
 Not for me. 

30
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:28,110
 Thinking about it now, 

31
00:03:28,110 --> 00:03:31,020
 we weren't really close at that time, either. 

32
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:32,980
 We just went to school together, 

33
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:35,800
 and after school, you ate at my house 
 and did your homework. 

34
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,600
 That's all. 

35
00:03:38,770 --> 00:03:41,560
 Maybe we did some special things together, 

36
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:46,319
 such as watching movies 
 or climbing mountains, 

37
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:50,400
 but I've done these things many times 
 with Yu Qiao and Du Shang. 

38
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:53,060
I only remember them…

39
00:03:57,240 --> 00:04:00,300
because when people are young, 
 their memory is especially good.

40
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:03,439
Still, even if we have no relationship,

41
00:04:04,330 --> 00:04:07,639
you shouldn't show that journal to others.

42
00:04:09,530 --> 00:04:12,150
It's very impolite,

43
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:15,190
and even rude.

44
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:21,339
Also, I've decided to transfer 
 to Experimental High School.

45
00:04:21,339 --> 00:04:25,859
This has nothing to do with you. 
 I simply need my friends,

46
00:04:25,859 --> 00:04:30,030
and you don't count as a friend.

47
00:04:31,380 --> 00:04:35,480
So from now on, if we meet again,

48
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,859
let's just pretend we are strangers,

49
00:04:40,859 --> 00:04:43,920
who never knew each other.

50
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,460
I understand.

51
00:04:56,970 --> 00:04:58,676
You can leave.

